#

Saffron Risotto with Grilled Asparagus

40 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main DishVegetarian

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodItalian

Description

A creamy and aromatic saffron risotto paired with perfectly grilled asparagus, delivering a delightful burst of flavor in every bite.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • saffron threads: 1 pinch
  • onion, finely chopped: 1 small
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • parmesan cheese, grated: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • asparagus, trimmed: 1 bunch
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
